ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
from o in ( from fp in FeedingPeriodFactory.Instance.GetAll(null) where fp.FeedingPeriodType != FeedingPeriodTypes.System
from m in FeedingPeriodFactory.Instance.ResetAndGetNextSchedule(fp).FeedingScheduleMixs select new { m.FeedingScheduleMixGID, m.Sequence, m.LoadDescription, fp.Company.CompanyName, fp.FeedingPeriodName, fp.FeedingPeriodGID, m.StartTime, m.Recipe.RecipeName, m.MixerEquipmentName, m.TargetAF, CapacityRemaining = (m.MaxMixCapacity * m.Recipe.DensityFactor) - m.TargetAF, RelativeStartDT = fp.StartTimeDT >= fp.Company.DayStartTimeDT ? new DateTime(1899,12,31).AddTicks(fp.StartTimeDT.Ticks) : new DateTime(1900, 1, 1).AddTicks(fp.StartTimeDT.Ticks), MixCount = FeedingPeriodFactory.Instance.NextSchedule(fp).FeedingScheduleMixs.Count() } ) {where} select new { o.FeedingScheduleMixGID, o.Sequence, o.CompanyName, o.FeedingPeriodName, o.FeedingPeriodGID, o.StartTime, o.RecipeName, o.MixerEquipmentName, o.TargetAF, o.CapacityRemaining, o.RelativeStartDT, o.LoadDescription, o.MixCount }
ReportQuery.SQLStatement:
select fp.FeedingPeriodGID ,fs.FeedingScheduleGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsm.LocationGID ,fsm.PlanRecipeGID ,fsm.Sequence ,r.RecipeGID
,fp.FeedingPeriodName ,c.CompanyName ,dbo.GetLoadDescription(fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID) as 'LoadDescription' ,r.RecipeName ,r.DensityFactor ,e.EquipmentNumber ,le.LocationName as 'EquipmentName'
,(select top 1 fsd.PlanStartTime from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm2 on fsm2.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID where fsm2.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID order by fsd.PlanStartTime) as 'StartTime'
,fs.FeedingScheduleType ,SumMix.SumAFLbs ,SumMix.SumAFKgs ,(dbo.GetMeasurementValue(e.MaxMixCapacityOz, 54) * r.DensityFactor) - SumMix.SumAFLbs as 'RemainingCapacityAFLbs' ,(dbo.GetMeasurementValue(e.MaxMixCapacityOz, 1056) * r.DensityFactor) - SumMix.SumAFKgs as 'RemainingCapacityAFKgs'
,case when fp.StartTime >= c.DayStartTime then dateadd(day, -1, convert(datetime, fp.StartTime)) else convert(datetime, fp.StartTime) end as 'RelativeStartDT'
from FeedingPeriod fp left join Company c on c.CompanyGID = fp.CompanyGID left join (select *, RowNum = ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by FeedingPeriodGID order by InstanceDate desc) from FeedingSchedule where InstanceDate < GETDATE() + 30) fs on fs.RowNum = 1 and fs.FeedingPeriodGID = fp.FeedingPeriodGID left join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleGID = fs.FeedingScheduleGID left join Recipe r on r.RecipeGID = fsm.PlanRecipeGID left join Location le on le.LocationGID = fsm.LocationGID left join EquipmentLocation el on el.LocationGID = le.LocationGID left join Equipment e on e.EquipmentGID = el.EquipmentGID left join (select mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(mi.TargetAFOz), 54) as SumAFLbs ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(mi.TargetAFOz), 1056) as SumAFKgs from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi group by mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID) SumMix on SumMix.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID
where (fp.FeedingPeriodType = 0 and fp.Inactive = 0)

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
from o in ( from fp in FeedingPeriodFactory.Instance.GetAll(null) where fp.FeedingPeriodType != FeedingPeriodTypes.System
from m in FeedingPeriodFactory.Instance.NextSchedule(fp).FeedingScheduleMixs from mi in m.FeedingScheduleMixInstructions select new { m.FeedingScheduleMixGID, fp.Company.CompanyName, fp.FeedingPeriodName, m.StartTime, m.Recipe.RecipeName, m.MixerEquipmentName, mi.DM_Pct, mi.Sequence, mi.TargetAF_MQty, InventoryItemName = mi.InventoryItem == null ? mi.RecipeInstruction.RecipeAction.ToString() : mi.InventoryItem.InventoryItemName, LocationName = mi.Location == null ? "" : mi.Location.LocationName, RunningTotal = m.FeedingScheduleMixInstructions.Where(x => x.Sequence <= mi.Sequence).Sum(z => z.TargetAF_MQty) } ) {where} select new { o.FeedingScheduleMixGID, o.CompanyName, o.FeedingPeriodName, o.StartTime, o.RecipeName, o.MixerEquipmentName, o.DM_Pct, o.Sequence, o.TargetAF_MQty, o.RunningTotal, o.InventoryItemName, o.LocationName }
ReportQuery.SQLStatement:
select fp.FeedingPeriodGID ,fs.FeedingScheduleGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID ,mi.RecipeInstructionGID
,mi.Sequence
,ii.InventoryItemName as 'Ingredient' ,li.LocationName as 'Location'
,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(mi.TargetAFOz, 54) as 'TargetAFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(mi.TargetAFOz, 1056) as 'TargetAFKgs'
,(select dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(mi2.TargetAFOz), 54) from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi2 where mi2.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID and mi2.Sequence <= mi.Sequence) as 'RunningTotalAFLbs'
,(select dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(mi2.TargetAFOz), 1056) from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi2 where mi2.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID and mi2.Sequence <= mi.Sequence) as 'RunningTotalAFKgs' ,fs.InstanceDate from FeedingPeriod fp join (select *, RowNum = ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by FeedingPeriodGID order by InstanceDate desc) from FeedingSchedule where InstanceDate < GETDATE() + 30) fs on fs.RowNum = 1 and fs.FeedingPeriodGID = fp.FeedingPeriodGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleGID = fs.FeedingScheduleGID join FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi on mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID join RecipeInstruction ri on ri.RecipeInstructionGID = mi.RecipeInstructionGID join InventoryItemLocation iil on iil.InventoryItemLocationGID = ri.InventoryItemLocationGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = iil.InventoryItemGID join Location li on li.LocationGID = iil.LocationGID
where (fp.FeedingPeriodType = 0 and fp.Inactive = 0 and fs.FeedingScheduleType != 100)

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
<QueryBundle> <QueryText>from o in ( from fp in FeedingPeriodFactory.Instance.GetAll(null) where fp.FeedingPeriodType != FeedingPeriodTypes.System
from m in FeedingPeriodFactory.Instance.NextSchedule(fp).FeedingScheduleMixs from d in m.FeedingScheduleDrops select new { m.FeedingScheduleMixGID, m.Recipe.RecipeName, fp.Company.CompanyName, fp.FeedingPeriodName, MixTotalAF = m.TargetAF, m.MixerEquipmentName, d.Pen.PenName, d.PenCount, d.PlanAF, d.Sequence, RemainingAF = m.TargetAF - m.FeedingScheduleDrops.Where(x => x.Sequence <= d.Sequence).Sum(z => z.PlanAF) } ) {where} select new { o.FeedingScheduleMixGID, o.CompanyName, o.FeedingPeriodName, o.RecipeName, o.MixerEquipmentName, o.MixTotalAF, o.PenName, o.PenCount, o.PlanAF, o.Sequence, o.RemainingAF }</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
ReportQuery.SQLStatement:
select fp.FeedingPeriodGID ,fs.FeedingScheduleGID ,fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID ,fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID ,fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID ,fsd.LocationGID
,fsd.Sequence ,lp.LocationName as 'Pen' ,Pen.PenNumber as 'PenNumber' ,(select top 1 pcc.[Count] from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = Pen.PenGID order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) as 'PenCount'
,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(fsd.PlanAFOz, 54) as 'PlanAFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(fsd.PlanAFOz, 1056) as 'PlanAFKgs' ,SumLoad.SumPlanAFLbs ,SumLoad.SumPlanAFKgs ,SumLoad.SumPlanAFLbs - (select SUM(dbo.GetMeasurementValue(fsd2.PlanAFOz, 54)) from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd2 where fsd2.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID and fsd2.Sequence <= fsd.Sequence) as 'RemainingAFLbs'
,SumLoad.SumPlanAFKgs - (select SUM(dbo.GetMeasurementValue(fsd2.PlanAFOz, 1056)) from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd2 where fsd2.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID and fsd2.Sequence <= fsd.Sequence) as 'RemainingAFKgs'
from FeedingPeriod fp join (select *, RowNum = ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by FeedingPeriodGID order by InstanceDate desc) from FeedingSchedule where InstanceDate < GETDATE() + 30) fs on fs.RowNum = 1 and fs.FeedingPeriodGID = fp.FeedingPeriodGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleGID = fs.FeedingScheduleGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd on fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join Location lp on lp.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join Pen on Pen.LocationGID = lp.LocationGID join (select fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(fsd.PlanAFOz), 54) as 'SumPlanAFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(fsd.PlanAFOz), 1056) as 'SumPlanAFKgs' from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd group by fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID) SumLoad on SumLoad.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID where (fp.FeedingPeriodType = 0 and fp.Inactive = 0 and fs.FeedingScheduleType != 100)
